#. Tag: title
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Skladnik is an implementation of the Japanese warehouse keeper game "
"“sokoban”."
msgstr "Skladnik je izvedba japonske igre skladiščnik “sokoban”."

#. Tag: para
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea is that you are a warehouse keeper trying to push crates to their "
"proper locations in a warehouse. The problem is that you cannot pull the "
"crates or step over them. If you are not careful, some of the crates can get "
"stuck in wrong places and/or block your way."
msgstr ""
"Ideja je, da ste skladiščnik, ki jim poskuša potisniti zaboje na ustrezne "
"lokacije v skladišču. Težava je v tem, da ne morete potegniti zabojev ali "
"stopiti čez njih. Če niste previdni, lahko dobite nekaj zabojev, ki so "
"obtičali na napačnih mestih in/ali vam blokirali pot."

#. Tag: title
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skladnik; is configured graphically, and does not have any commandline "
"options other than the standard &kf6-full; and &Qt; options."
msgstr ""
"&skladnik; je konfiguriran grafično in nima ukazne vrstice za možnosti, ki "
"niso standardne &kf6-full; in možnosti &Qt;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skladnik; options"
msgstr "&skladnik; možnosti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "--help"
msgstr "--help"

#. Tag: para
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display help and exit."
msgstr "Prikaži pomoč in končaj."

#. Tag: option
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "--help-all"
msgstr "--help-all"

#. Tag: para
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays help including Qt specific options."
msgstr "Prikaže pomoč, vključno s posebnimi možnostmi Qt."

#. Tag: option
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "--version"
msgstr "--version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-skladnik.6.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show version and exit."
msgstr "Prikaži različico in končaj."

